Package uk.co.crider.jablus.data.store

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionIO
    Used to store and retrive agent actions during a simulation
    CSVFile
    A file to read and write CSV data.
    DataSetIO
    Provides methods for loading and saving DataSet objects from disk NOTE: + Any DataSets containing datasets will be written to a different CSV file + Each DataSet is associated with its own CSV file, with the same name as that dataset + DataSets are not allowed to be un-named
    DataTable
    Stores table-based data, which can be saved directly as CSV
    History
    Stores all simulation data in temporal snapshots and stores them to disk
    RandomLineAccessFile
    Allows simultaneous line-wise reading and writing of data Read access is random, while write access is sequential
    TupleData
